outputs.output_descr: This project was created to receive the Common Humanitarian Funds (CHF) allocated to the Office of RC/HC in Sudan for both the North and South. Later the South fund component were moved to a different project and this project is now for the Three Areas.
NFIs, Common Services and Coordination enhanced for Emergency Responses in Southern Sudan with the support of Common Humanitarian Fund (CHF)
outputs.output_title: CHF fund to ORCHC in South Sud
